Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • Employee
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Employee>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Faculty, Staff
    public abstract class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Employee>, java.lang.Cloneable
    The Employee class is a super class that is the parent class to Staff, and Faculty It must be an abstract class due to being a super class and must implement comparable, cloneable and Employee_Info.

    Osman
